śHAROLD ARTHUR DUDMAN:
MARCH 5TH 1923 - JUNE 6TH 2009
FREEMAN OF THE CITY OF LONDON,
WANDSMAN OF
ST. PAUL'S CATHEDRAL

[Second inscription added 2019]
ALSO HIS BELOVED WIFE
OF 58 YEARS
EDITH IRENE (LESLEY) DUDMAN
JANUARY 26TH 1926 - MARCH 24TH 2019
REUNITED FOR ETERNITY"Ø
Ü[SEAT BACK]
WILLIAM McLEAN MUSICIAN 1904 - 1989
BELOVED HUSBAND OF JOY McLEAN (Prof. Kn' as SANDRA WELLS) 

[UNDER SEAT]
REMEMBERED IN SO MANY HEARTS"Ī
×Dedicated to the memory of
Rene Tkacik
who lost his life working in the Crossrail tunnels
on the 7th of March 2014
from his family, friends and colleagues"ó
¤To the very dear memory of
Hannelore Nath "Anne"
who loved London and the changing of
the seasons in its beautiful parks and squares
Danzig 1932    London 2009"ż
ĪMATT SKELTON
(13 Oct 1966 - 27 July 2009)
