To laugh and talk on Sammy's seat
In loving memory of
Samantha Jane Thompson 1981 - 2009
She brought laughter into our lives
and love into our hearts"╚
┼In memory of
Dr Thomas Schofield
who worked in Queen Square from 2004-2010
All of old. Nothing else ever. Ever tried. Ever failed
No matter. Try again. Fail again
Fail better
(Samuel Beckett)"╠
